# The backend API URL this deployment talks to (no trailing slash).
# This is a BUILD-TIME variable — Vite bakes it into the compiled JS, so it
# must be set in Render's Environment tab for the frontend Static Site
# BEFORE each build/deploy, not changed afterward at runtime.
#
# If left unset, the login screen's "API server URL" field starts blank and
# whoever opens the app for the first time must type it in manually (it's
# then remembered in that browser via localStorage).
VITE_API_URL=https://your-clinic-backend.onrender.com
